Expected Result:
1.List of beneficiaries is displayed correctly



TS-08 Verify editing beneficiary details

TC-08.1 Edit beneficiary name

Steps:
1.Select existing beneficiary
2.Edit beneficiary name
3.Save changes


Expected Result:
1.Beneficiary details are updated successfully

TS-09 Verify deleting beneficiary

TC-09.1 Delete beneficiary confirmation

Steps:
1.Select beneficiary
2.Click Delete
3.Confirm deletion


Expected Result:
1.Beneficiary is removed from the list


TS-10 Verify duplicate beneficiary addition

TC-10.1 Add existing beneficiary again

Steps:
1.Add beneficiary with same account details


Expected Result:
1.Duplicate beneficiary error is shown



TS-11 Verify beneficiary activation time

TC-11.1 Cool-off period validation

Expected Result:
1.Beneficiary becomes active only after configured time


TS-12 Verify unauthorized access

TC-12.1 Access without login

Steps:
1.Access beneficiary URL directly


Expected Result:
1.User is redirected to login page



TS-13 Verify session timeout

TC-13.1 Session expires during add beneficiary


Expected Result:
1.User is logged out
2.Session expired message is displayed


TS-14 Verify service unavailability handling

TC-14.1 Beneficiary service down

Expected Result:
1.Proper error message is displayed
2.No data loss occurs




